Rajae Imran ma ọ bụ Raja Imrane (Arabic) bụ onye Morocco na-eme ihe nkiri na onye bụbu onye nta akụkọ.

A maara Rajae Imran nke ọma maka ọrụ ya dị mkpa na usoro TV Al Mostadaafoun (المستضعفون, The Underdogs) dịka Aicha na onye na-eme ihe nkiri Rachid El Ouali, nke bụ ngosipụta mbụ ya. Ọ rụkwara ọrụ n'ọtụtụ ihe nkiri Moroccan dịka Aalach ya waldi ?, Wahda men Bezzaf, Machaf Mara.
